node.text:
🤹🏽‍♂️ JUGGLING FIVE 🤹🏽‍♂️  
It can be said that one of the most important aspects of brewing the perfect IPA is the Hops. What you choose, how much of it you use, and when you use it is a delicate dance which has a drastic effect on the taste, turbidity, and aroma of an IPA, and consequently the overall experience and balance of the beer🍺 🍺 🍺 🍺 🍺

We’ve aim at staying trippy when it comes to hops by using experimentals, playing with proportions, tweaking our hop schedules, all that jazzy stuff. We’ve come to really love a specific handful of them, so we went for a tripping 🤯 FIRST 🤯 and threw all 🚨FIVE 🚨 of the bad boys into a DIPA. You’ll have a tropical rainforest of aromatics and notes, rounded out with a distinct crisp dryness.

Its hard enough juggling a few, but imagine 

💚🐒 💚🐒 💚🐒💚
🐒 JUGGLING FIVE 🐒
💚🐒 💚🐒 💚🐒💚
Double India Pale Ale Hopped with Lotus, Citra, Motueka, Cashmere, and Lemondrop Hops

$20/4pk

8.5 % ABV

🆕PRE-ORDER FOR “ JUGGLING FIVE “ BEGINS SUNDAY, AUGUST 22ND @ 4:20PM 👀

📦Pick-Up Starts TUESDAY, August 24th @ 4:00PM💨

Never dropping a single hop with this one
And as always, 

✌🏽&❤️

#StayTrippy #JugglingFive

node.text:
🌎HAPPY EARTHSTRONG VANE🌎

Today we celebrate a solar-return that sits on the dark side of the sun, for none other than princess of darkness herself, Vanessa!

Do you know Vanessa?🤔🤔
If you don’t, she’s our 🥀 🥀 black dahlia flower bartender from the underworld 🥀🥀 She oozes total badassery and don’t F*$k with me vibes and we’re forever here for it because as we all know, this industry can get pretty wild from time to time. Her straight-to-the-point attitude and confidence is undoubtedly part of her charm and there is never a dull moment as long as she’s around, probably somewhere sipping some coffee ( with no sugar ) or practicing the dark arts

🎉 🎉 Happy Birthday, Vane 🎉 🎉
We wish you many more years of tasteful mischief and church services at la playa 🏝 
❤️ ❤️ ❤️ ❤️ ❤️ ❤️We love you❤️  ❤️ ❤️ ❤️ ❤️ ❤️ 
Drop all your love, new spells, and serial killer references/knowledge below! 
And as always, 

✌🏽&🖤

#HappyBirthday #felizcumpleaños

node.text:
🦘KOO KOO KANGA SHAKE🦘

Have you been enjoying all our recent and divinely delectable MILKSHAKE sours?? Well, we certainly know a certain kangaroo that has gone beyond bonkers for the sensational stuff, so we just had to make them a shake all their own and you would NOT believe what this mesmerized marsupial enjoys🤯

We threw enough apricots and cherries into this shake to cover the entirety of a desert, gave it some chocolate and vanilla lovin, and shaved some coconut and hazelnut atop its billowy milkshake goodness😍😍  our eyes are swirling😵‍💫😵‍💫
because this is sure one..

🥥🌰🍒🍫🥥🌰🍒🍫🥥🌰
🍫KOO KOO KANGA SHAKE🍒
🥥🌰🍒🍫🥥🌰🍒🍫🥥🌰 
Milkshake-inspired Sour Ale Conditioned with Cherries, Apricots, Coconut, Hazelnut, Chocolate, Vanilla, and Milk Sugar.  $22/4pk

6% ABV

🆕PRE-ORDER FOR “ KOO KOO KANGA SHAKE “ BEGINS SUNDAY, AUGUST 22ND, @ 4:20PM 👀

📦Pick-Up Starts TUESDAY, August 24TH @ 4:00PM💨

node.text:
🌎HAPPY EARTHSTRONG CHUCHO🌎  Today we celebrate a very special solar return that is near and extremely dear to our hearts, for none other than the sensei himself, CHUCHO!  Chucho has the spirit and heart of 💪🏽10 men💪🏽& 🦁30 lions 🦁combined. He lives and breathes loyalty and love for everyone he considers family, never wavering in making someone laugh or smile. Chucho has been here with us, helping build our tripping universe, since day one and his wisdom, clear-minded vision, and compassion has had a lasting impact and influence on what Tripping Animals is today.  
Chucho, the brewery lifestyle wouldn’t be the same with out your boisterous laugh and all the dancing you do when listening to some of your favorite Ska music, we hope you keep bringing your boogie and incredible vibes for years to come

Cheers to Master Chucho! Mentor, father, brother , amigo
🎉 🎉 🎉 Happy Birthday x 100000🎉 🎉 🎉

❤️ ❤️ ❤️ ❤️ ❤️
❤️We love you ❤️ 
❤️ ❤️ ❤️ ❤️ ❤️

Drop all your love, ska band recommendations, and funny meme references for him in the comments!

#MasterChucho # HappyBirthday

node.text:
🐿DROP THE PRESSURE🐿

As we draw closer and closer to fall, all the end of the year festivities come to mind: Oktoberfest, our anniversary, Christmas, and of course New Years. So we’re cranking up the volume but never cracking under pressure as we start to drop banger after banger 🕺🏽

Although this little furry mammal may be small in size, he doesn’t disappoint in the flavor he brings. Heaps upon heaps of raspberry and pineapple  swirl through this OG sour, infused with that delightful vanilla and marshmallow goodness we have all come to love 😍

Only one thing left to do..

🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿
🍍DROP THE PRESSURE🍍
🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿
Sour Ale Conditioned it’s Raspberry, Pineapple, Vanilla, and Marshmallow

$22/4pk

6% ABV

🆕PRE-ORDER FOR “DROP THE PRESSURE“ BEGINS TOMORROW @ 4:20PM 👀

📦Pick-Up Starts TUESDAY,  August 17th @ 4:00PM💨

Loving the pressure with this one 
And as always, 

✌🏽&❤️

#StayTrippy #DropThePressure

node.text:
💡ITS SHOWTIME💡

Being able to bring back some OG’s, especially one done with homies like @corporateladderbrewing , is always a great feeling for a brewery familia. It signifies you’ve allowed us to go about making outlandish beers long enough to circle back around and drop a re-release, that you’ve stuck by our side and embarked on this trip with us, and we must continue to trust in the process and enjoy the sights along the way.

Bigger, badder, bolder, heavier handed, because why not? But rather because we must. The only thing to do is to stare into the spotlight and give it more than before; This cockatoo has come to do just that. More pineapple, more Peach, more Florida blossom honey.

Back for an encore 🎭

🍑 🍍 🍑 🍍 🍑 🍍 
🍍IT’S SHOWTIME🍑
🍑 🍍 🍑 🍍 🍑 🍍 
Sour Ale Conditioned with Pineapple, Peach, and Florida Blossom Honey

$22/4pk

6%

🆕PRE-ORDER FOR “ IT’S SHOWTIME “ BEGINS SUNDAY, AUGUST 15TH, @ 4:20PM 👀

📦Pick-Up Starts TUESDAY, August 17th @ 4:00PM💨

Back on stage with this one
And as always, 

✌🏽&❤️

#StayTrippy #It’sShowtime #Collab #CorporateLadder
